---
/**
 * AboutIntro — основной блок страницы About.
 *
 * Структура (узлы Figma 1:6880 + 1:6855):
 *  - Большой H1 "If you're ready to unlock your full potential..." центрированный,
 *    5 строк, font-heading 62px. В Figma узлы 1:6881-1:6885 показывают
 *    конкретное разбиение строк (но в HTML дадим браузеру решать сам).
 *  - Body text — 3 параграфа, центрированный по странице, max-width ~900px.
 *
 * Фон секции — cream (Rectangle 5, узел 1:6853, h=1061).
 */
---

<section
  class="w-full bg-cream py-24"
  data-section="about-intro"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-design px-[7.55%]">
    {/* Большой центрированный заголовок */}
    <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-[1177px] text-center font-heading text-h1 uppercase text-gold leading-tight">
      If you're ready to unlock your full potential, it's time to discover the unique wellness and weight loss solutions offered by Ideal Medical &amp; Wellness.
    </h2>

    {/* Body — 3 параграфа, центрированы, max-width 902px (узел 1:6855) */}
    <div class="mx-auto mt-20 max-w-[902px] space-y-6 text-center font-sans text-body-lg text-gold leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Our team is dedicated to providing personalized experiences and excellence in wellness. We are redefining healthcare with our concierge services, tailored specifically to your needs, ensuring you receive the highest level of care.
      </p>
      <p>
        At Ideal Medical &amp; Wellness, our team is committed to creating a professional, trusting environment. We stay at the forefront of wellness and weight loss innovations to ensure you always feel valued and understood. Discretion is a key pillar of our service, and we guarantee the highest level of confidentiality.
      </p>
      <p>
        The Ideal Medical &amp; Wellness team brings extensive expertise, education, and skills, making us the top choice in medical wellness, especially for professional athletes and patients who are committed to achieving the best possible results. While customization is an integral part of our mission, we also center our treatments around proven and effective ones. Together, we can help you navigate your wellness journey with our signature treatments designed to enhance your well-being.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
